{"id":341011,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/04/茂名政府px事件发布会疑被指为自编自导/","date":"2014-04-03T22:17:56Z","modified":"2014-04-03T22:17:56Z","title":"茂名政府PX事件发布会疑被指为自编自导","content":"<p>4月3日，原本定于4日召开的<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/04/%E8%B4%A2%E7%BB%8F%E7%BD%91-%E8%8C%82%E5%90%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%9A%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%AF%AF%E4%BC%A4%E4%BA%86%E5%9B%B4%E8%A7%82%E7%BE%A4%E4%BC%97/\">茂名市政府PX事件新闻发布会</a>突然在提前一天举行。同时<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20140403/bkncn-20140403224555641-0403_05011_001.html\">有报道称</a>发布会当天现场外戒备森严，只有获邀请的记者才可以参加，而原先预告的网络视频直播最后变成了文字直播。</p>\n<p>当天亦有新浪微博用户曝光称该新闻发布会早已事先安排、分配好问题，并经过彩排后才开始，实为茂名政府自编自导的一场表演。</p>\n<p>图片来源：新浪微博 <a href=\"http://weibo.com/230120102\">@-X_JN-</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/04/8f72833fjw1ef2v71oozvj20ad35fk5j.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-341012\" alt=\"8f72833fjw1ef2v71oozvj20ad35fk5j\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/04/8f72833fjw1ef2v71oozvj20ad35fk5j.jpg\" width=\"373\" height=\"4083\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/04/8f72833fjw1ef2u7ysjmvj20gm18g7bx.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-341013\" alt=\"8f72833fjw1ef2u7ysjmvj20gm18g7bx\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/04/8f72833fjw1ef2u7ysjmvj20gm18g7bx.jpg\" width=\"478\" height=\"1280\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/04/8f72833fjw1ef2u7ysjmvj20gm18g7bx.jpg 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/04/8f72833fjw1ef2u7ysjmvj20gm18g7bx-112x300.jpg 112w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/04/8f72833fjw1ef2u7ysjmvj20gm18g7bx-382x1024.jpg 382w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 478px) 100vw, 478px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[18810,9006,24910]}